---
title: "_applyFeedInfoUpdates (PriceManager)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_empty: check adds and removes
    q_check_empty --> q_error_empty: both empty
    q_error_empty --> [*]: revert EmptyList
    q_check_empty --> q_remove_loop: at least one non-empty
    q_remove_loop --> q_on_update_rm: for each asset to remove
    q_on_update_rm --> q_remove_asset: _onFeedInfoUpdate(asset, true)
    q_remove_asset --> q_error_not_allowed: !allowlisted
    q_error_not_allowed --> [*]: revert AssetNotAllowlisted
    q_remove_asset --> q_cleanup: allowlisted, removed
    q_cleanup --> q_remove_loop: delete feedId mapping, feedInfo, price
    q_remove_loop --> q_add_loop: removals done
    q_add_loop --> q_on_update_add: for each feedInfo to add
    q_on_update_add --> q_check_asset_zero: _onFeedInfoUpdate(asset, false)
    q_check_asset_zero --> q_error_zero_addr: asset == address(0)
    q_error_zero_addr --> [*]: revert InvalidZeroAddress
    q_check_asset_zero --> q_check_feeds: asset != address(0)
    q_check_feeds --> q_error_zero_val: stalenessThreshold == 0 AND both feed sources zero
    q_error_zero_val --> [*]: revert InvalidZeroValue
    q_check_feeds --> q_check_streams: valid feed config
    q_check_streams --> q_check_version: dataStreamsFeedId != 0
    q_check_version --> q_error_version: version != 3
    q_error_version --> [*]: revert InvalidFeedVersion
    q_check_version --> q_check_rotation: version == 3
    q_check_rotation --> q_handle_rotation: previousAsset != address(0) AND previousAsset != asset
    q_handle_rotation --> q_update_mapping: clear previous asset streams data
    q_check_rotation --> q_update_mapping: no rotation needed
    q_update_mapping --> q_store: update feedId to asset mapping
    q_check_streams --> q_store: dataStreamsFeedId == 0
    q_store --> q_add_loop: s_feedInfo[asset] = feedInfo
    q_add_loop --> [*]: all adds processed

    note right of q_check_rotation
        INV-001: Feed ID rotation clears previous asset streams state
        INV-002: Previous asset must retain data feed if streams feed is rotated away
        INV-003: Only v3 Data Streams reports are supported
        INV-004: Staleness threshold must be non-zero
        INV-005: BaseAuction override prevents changes during live auctions
    end note
